  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forest swamp</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> pleasant vegetation, splashing through water, the soothing chomping of crocodiles and the snorting of hippos — Bob loves the calm of this place </li><li> a changing time of day, but a clock is always close at hand </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> duel with global matchmaking </li><li> sparring between friends </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rules</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> with rebirth boulders, Bob can keep living, resurrecting again and again </li><li> after a win, you can carry out any items from duels and sparring, except boulders — as many as you can hold; take them into other matches or bring them back to Camp </li><li> you can add the offender or the defeated to friends and continue in sparring — because how could anyone say no to Bob </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attacks</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> boulder throw </li><li> kick strike </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot in duels and sparring</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> barrels that always contain something to eat </li><li> pack-tents with gear and supplies </li><li> barbed wire stakes — stop animals and discourage excessive kicking </li><li> firewood you will also find a use for </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stamina system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Bob used to allow himself excess, but that is in the past: all food is healthy, and everything is put to use </li><li> food restores not only the urge to kick, but also grip </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inventory</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> inventory tiles for placing clothing, facial expressions, and food </li><li> unique facial expressions reflect the boundless range of moods of the swamp’s owner </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swamp dwellers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> mostly harmless hippos and crocodiles drain stamina </li><li> they love tents, but hate open fire </li><li> they chew on your gear, but you are unlikely to be able to punish them for it </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forest swamp</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> pleasant vegetation, splashing through water, the soothing chomping of crocodiles and the snorting of hippos — Bob loves the calm of this place </li><li> a changing time of day, but a clock is always close at hand </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/bde633e310a08a889a4a0349ee350e32.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> duel with global matchmaking </li><li> sparring between friends </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/740f8b442d640ad902d8d6177c7e0be7.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rules</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> with rebirth boulders, Bob can keep living, resurrecting again and again </li><li> after a win, you can carry out any items from duels and sparring, except boulders — as many as you can hold; take them into other matches or bring them back to Camp </li><li> you can add the offender or the defeated to friends and continue in sparring — because how could anyone say no to Bob </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attacks</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> boulder throw </li><li> kick strike </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/567352bc3a4eaa44e184b0966f98a705.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot in duels and sparring</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> barrels that always contain something to eat </li><li> pack-tents with gear and supplies </li><li> barbed wire stakes — stop animals and discourage excessive kicking </li><li> firewood you will also find a use for </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stamina system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Bob used to allow himself excess, but that is in the past: all food is healthy, and everything is put to use </li><li> food restores not only the urge to kick, but also grip </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inventory</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> inventory tiles for placing clothing, facial expressions, and food </li><li> unique facial expressions reflect the boundless range of moods of the swamp’s owner </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.poster.avif?t=1770481797\" width=1170 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.webm?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792220/extras/d49f37ff70c314bf059aa630af591ef0.mp4?t=1770481797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swamp dwellers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> mostly harmless hippos and crocodiles drain stamina </li><li> they love tents, but hate open fire </li><li> they chew on your gear, but you are unlikely to be able to punish them for it </li></ul>",
